StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: INSERTADMIN
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.INSERTADMIN(pFirstName IN VARCHAR2, pSurname IN VARCHAR2,&lt;br/&gt;pTitle IN VARCHAR2, pAddress IN VARCHAR2, pPhone IN NUMBER, pPostcode IN NUMBER,&lt;br/&gt;pCampusLocation IN VARCHAR2, pIdBuilding IN VARCHAR2, pNumberOffice IN VARCHAR2, pStaffType IN VARCHAR2,&lt;br/&gt;pAdminTitle IN VARCHAR2, pComputerSkill IN VARCHAR2, pOfficeSkill IN VARCHAR2) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; INSERT INTO Admin_table &lt;br/&gt; VALUES(Admin_obj(sequenceAdminID.Nextval, pSurname, pFirstName, pTitle, pAddress, pPhone, pPostcode, &lt;br/&gt; pCampusLocation, pIdBuilding, pNumberOffice, pStaffType, pAdminTitle, pComputerSkill, pOfficeSkill));&lt;br/&gt; COMMIT;&lt;br/&gt;END insertAdmin;
